# 🚀 AWS S3 Static Website Hosting using Terraform

## 📌 Project Description

This project demonstrates how to host a static website on AWS S3 using Terraform.

The workflow includes:

* Creating an S3 bucket
* Configuring public access
* Applying a bucket policy
* Enabling static website hosting
* Uploading HTML files using Terraform
* Outputting the website endpoint

---

## 🧠 Objective

To understand how to:

* Use Terraform to provision AWS resources
* Configure S3 for static website hosting
* Automate file uploads using Terraform

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

```
User → S3 Static Website Endpoint → S3 Bucket → HTML Files
```

